 perpetual and spot prices across major exchanges. The platform applies a dampening factor to reduce extreme rates during high volatility periods. Funding is exchanged between long and short position holders at each 8-hour interval, with rates typically ranging from -0.375% to +0.375% per cycle. BingX's copy trading feature can amplify funding rate impacts as followers mirror positions en masse."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
